EN: I didn't sleep well last night, so it's hard for me to wake up this morning.

ZH: 刚才我差点就要睡着了，但是我强迫自己苏醒。
EN: I was about to fall asleep just now, but I forced myself to stay awake.

ZH: 这个咖啡很强，喝完后你会立即苏醒的。
EN: This coffee is strong, you will immediately wake up after drinking it.

